Anda tahu perbezaan sentuhan 
menyebabkan perbezaan bunyi…

53
00:04:48,204 --> 00:04:50,540
- Ya, Jung-hyun. 
- Tuan di mana?

54
00:04:50,623 --> 00:04:52,834
Ada kes. Tuan perlu ke balai.

55
00:04:52,917 --> 00:04:55,503
Suami Yoon Seo-ha ditemui mati.

56
00:04:57,630 --> 00:05:00,883
Maksud awak, dia dah meninggal?

57
00:05:02,218 --> 00:05:04,220
- Ya. 
- Bagaimana dia meninggal?

58
00:05:09,851 --> 00:05:11,269
Baiklah.

