kemungkinan dia guna senapang memburu.

66
00:05:52,185 --> 00:05:53,478
Sampai akhir…

67
00:05:59,067 --> 00:05:59,901
Baik,

68
00:06:01,235 --> 00:06:03,112
saya akan tanya soalan.

69
