boleh buktikan waktu awak sampai di rumah?

91
00:07:22,358 --> 00:07:24,485
Ada rakaman keselamatan apartmen?

92
00:07:28,239 --> 00:07:29,907
Awak mengesyaki saya?

93
00:07:31,284 --> 00:07:34,036
Kami hanya menyiasat, puan.

94
00:07:39,375 --> 00:07:40,585
Kim Young-ho?

95
00:07:41,169 --> 00:07:42,420
Siapa?

96
00:07:42,503 --> 00:07:45,965
Lelaki yang mengaku dia adik tiri saya. 
Dah siasat dia?

97
00:07:46,924 --> 00:07:48,593
Ya. Kami dah soal dia.

98
00:07:48,676 --> 00:07:51,512
Dia keluar dengan kawan dia ketika itu,

99
00:07:51,596 --> 00:07:54,182
dan alibi dia telah disahkan.

100
00:07:54,891 --> 00:07:55,850
Awak yakin?

101
00:07:57,602 --> 00:07:59,645
Awak yakin tentang itu?

102
00:08:09,071 --> 00:08:11,324
Pandu selamat. Kami akan hubungi awak.

103
00:08:11,407 --> 00:08:12,241
Baik.

104
00:09:34,865 --> 00:09:37,702
THE BEQUEATHED

105
00:10:28,294 --> 00:10:30,796
Biar betul. Sakit hati aku.

106
00:10:31,464 --> 00:10:33,549
Siapa benarkan dia masuk?

107
00:10:35,718 --> 00:10:38,387
Detektif Choi, 
saya suruh awak tunggu di luar.

108
00:10:38,471 --> 00:10:41,724
Saya akan jelaskan segalanya. 
Kenapa awak masuk ke sini?

109
00:10:42,224 --> 00:10:46,395
"Dengar penjelasan biasa-biasa, 
tengok mayat baru luar biasa.

110
00:10:46,479 --> 00:10:47,897
Bedebah bodoh."

111
00:10:47,980 --> 00:10:49,065
Ulang sekali lagi?

112
00:10:49,565 --> 00:10:53,027
Pesanan awak 20 tahun lalu. 
Pesanan yang teramat bijak.

113
00:10:53,110 --> 00:10:54,612
Bangsat.

114
00:10:55,321 --> 00:10:58,491
Tutup mulut dan tengok. 
Jangan makan di depan mayat.

115
00:10:58,574 --> 00:11:01,952
Saya tidak boleh fokus. 
Kuat sangat awak kunyah.

116
00:11:02,036 --> 00:11:03,204
Sedap sangat.

117
00:11:04,664 --> 00:11:05,998
Baru makan. Dah habis.

118
00:11:06,666 --> 00:11:07,541
Apa-apalah.

119
00:11:10,169 --> 00:11:12,088
Jadi? Ada petunjuk?

120
00:11:12,588 --> 00:11:16,926
Pelet senapang yang digelar buckshot, 
selalunya untuk tembak haiwan.

121
00:11:17,009 --> 00:11:19,428
Buckshot? Selain itu?

122
00:11:19,512 --> 00:11:22,723
Lelasan akibat rumput 
atau batu kerikil di belakang.

123
00:11:22,807 --> 00:11:25,726
Nampaknya dalang itu 
heret dia dan buang dia.

124
00:11:26,268 --> 00:11:27,895
Maknanya,

125
00:11:27,978 --> 00:11:31,399
kita mungkin boleh jumpa 
DNA pesalah pada bahagian leher.

126
00:11:33,234 --> 00:11:35,986
- Maknanya tiada jawapan. 
- Betul itu.

127
00:11:36,570 --> 00:11:39,073
Kenapa awak teruja macam dah ada jawapan?

128
00:11:39,156 --> 00:11:41,158
Sensitif sangat.

129
00:11:41,742 --> 00:11:46,163
Katanya balai awak akan kurangkan orang.

130
00:11:46,706 --> 00:11:48,207
Ya? Saya tidak tahu pun.

131
00:11:48,791 --> 00:11:51,419
Mereka akan menstruktur semula pasukan.

132
00:11:53,879 --> 00:11:56,215
Mungkin kerana populasi semakin kurang.

133
00:11:56,716 --> 00:11:59,677
Kes pembunuhan jarang berlaku 
di kawasan kampung.

134
00:12:00,428 --> 00:12:01,470
Apa-apa pun,

135
00:12:03,139 --> 00:12:04,098
jika benar,

136
00:12:04,640 --> 00:12:07,435
Park Sang-min yang lengai 
mungkin akan terkesan.

137
00:12:08,310 --> 00:12:10,813
Khabar angin dah tersebar, mungkin benar.

138
00:12:11,313 --> 00:12:15,025
Tapi hidup awak lebih mudah 
jika Park dipecat, betul?

139
00:12:15,526 --> 00:12:17,528
Apa yang awak merepek ini?

140
00:12:18,237 --> 00:12:20,406
Jangan mengarut, fokus pada kerja!

141
00:12:20,489 --> 00:12:22,074
Jaga adab. Saya lebih tua.

142
00:12:22,158 --> 00:12:23,826
Perangai macam budak-budak!

143
00:12:25,619 --> 00:12:27,204
Jaga tepi kain orang.

144
00:12:28,622 --> 00:12:29,665
Maaf.

145
00:12:32,001 --> 00:12:33,836
Saya hanya kasihankan dia.

146
00:12:48,184 --> 00:12:49,101
Tuan.

147
00:12:54,315 --> 00:12:58,778
Kami akan siasat kes Yang Jae-seok 
dan Yoon Myung-gil secara berasingan.

148
00:12:59,278 --> 00:13:00,279
Baik, teruskan.

149
00:13:03,032 --> 00:13:04,742
Laporan Choi Sung-jun, betul?

150
00:13:05,743 --> 00:13:08,662
Dia memang pandai menulis laporan

151
00:13:08,746 --> 00:13:11,499
dengan ketepatan gaya tentera.

152
00:13:15,211 --> 00:13:20,591
PEJABAT KETUA

153
00:13:23,135 --> 00:13:26,305
Tuan. Katanya Detektif Park 
mungkin akan dipecat

154
00:13:26,388 --> 00:13:28,224
semasa penstrukturan semula.

155
00:13:28,849 --> 00:13:29,809
Mustahil, betul?

156
00:13:30,810 --> 00:13:33,896
Dia selesaikan seluruh kes ini.

157
00:13:33,979 --> 00:13:36,816
Bukankah Detektif Choi yang patut dipecat?

158
00:13:36,899 --> 00:13:37,733
Hei.

159
00:13:38,234 --> 00:13:41,320
Awak rasa bos 
yang selesaikan kes Yoon Myung-gil?

160
00:13:41,821 --> 00:13:42,655
Ya.

161
00:13:43,906 --> 00:13:46,408
Sung-jun yang selesaikan segalanya.

162
00:13:47,201 --> 00:13:48,118
Maksud awak?

163
00:13:48,202 --> 00:13:50,538
Detektif Park tulis laporan kes,

164
00:13:50,621 --> 00:13:53,791
dan Detektif Choi merayau-rayau 
tanpa arah tuju.

165
00:13:53,874 --> 00:13:59,213
Sung-jun siasat dan selesaikan 
semua kes Detektif Park.

166
00:13:59,296 --> 00:14:01,048
Dah lama macam itu.

167
00:14:01,549 --> 00:14:05,052
Jika mahu buang orang, 
lebih baik buang Detektif Park.

168
00:14:05,135 --> 00:14:08,347
Jika Sung-jun dipecat 
hanya kerana aspek luaran,

169
00:14:08,430 --> 00:14:10,683
tentu sangat teruk dan tidak adil.

170
00:14:10,766 --> 00:14:15,187
Jadi, Detektif Choi uruskan kes, 
tapi Detektif Park yang dapat nama.

171
00:14:15,271 --> 00:14:17,857
Macam itulah selama ini?

172
00:14:18,649 --> 00:14:21,151
Tentu ada sesuatu berlaku antara mereka.

173
00:14:22,820 --> 00:14:25,990
Mereka berdua rapat macam adik-beradik

174
00:14:26,073 --> 00:14:28,158
sebelum kejadian itu.

175
00:14:47,219 --> 00:14:51,807
Anak Sung-jun suka melepak 
dengan budak-budak bermasalah.

176
00:14:53,642 --> 00:14:57,897
Kemudian budak-budak itu tahu 
yang ayah dia pegawai polis,

177
00:14:57,980 --> 00:15:00,399
jadi mereka mula membuli dia.

178
00:15:02,318 --> 00:15:05,154
Mungkin mereka mencabar satu sama lain.

179
00:15:05,779 --> 00:15:06,697
Jun-hyung.

180
00:15:07,698 --> 00:15:08,616
Choi Jun-hyung.

181
00:15:41,190 --> 00:15:43,609
Sial! Itu saja kemampuan kau?

182
00:15:44,526 --> 00:15:46,779
Itu saja? Biar betul?

183
00:15:47,905 --> 00:15:48,906
Hei!

184
00:15:48,989 --> 00:15:52,326
Jika kau bukan musuh kami, tikam ayah kau!

185
00:15:52,826 --> 00:15:54,244
Pengecut!

186
00:16:03,712 --> 00:16:06,757
Bagus! Itu baru betul. Celaka!

187
00:16:10,302 --> 00:16:11,387
Sial!

188
00:16:24,608 --> 00:16:25,442
Jun-hyung.

189
00:16:28,779 --> 00:16:31,240
Kenapa kamu buat begini?

190
00:16:31,824 --> 00:16:35,786
Jadi Detektif Park yang tercedera, 
bukannya Sung-jun.

191
00:16:37,913 --> 00:16:39,331
Saya tengok berita.

192
00:16:39,415 --> 00:16:42,126
Itu kisah Detektif Park dan Detektif Choi?

193
00:16:45,421 --> 00:16:49,466
Selepas itu, kaki Detektif Park tempang.

194
00:16:50,050 --> 00:16:54,388
Kemudian, dia tidak keruan, 
sehingga isteri dia ceraikan dia.

195
00:16:56,432 --> 00:16:59,184
Sekarang, dia tidak boleh jumpa anak-anak.

196
00:16:59,268 --> 00:17:02,938
Bagaimana dengan anak Detektif Choi? 
Di mana dia sekarang?

197
00:17:03,981 --> 00:17:05,232
Mungkin di penjara.

198
00:17:05,315 --> 00:17:08,902
Waktu itu dia masih pelajar. 
Mungkin lima tahun penjara.

199
00:17:09,695 --> 00:17:11,947
Saya tidak sangka. Ya Tuhan.

200
00:17:12,031 --> 00:17:15,534
Tapi mereka masih bekerja 
dalam pasukan yang sama.

201
00:17:16,285 --> 00:17:18,620
Takdir yang malang.

202
00:17:19,204 --> 00:17:23,208
Maknanya ada kemungkinan 
Detektif Park akan dipecat?

203
00:17:23,292 --> 00:17:26,545
Itu bukan tugas awak. 
Diam dan jangan cari masalah.

204
00:17:26,628 --> 00:17:28,881
- Kita perlu tahu semua ini… 
- Tuan.

205
00:17:31,508 --> 00:17:33,594
Kamu dah makan?

206
00:17:34,386 --> 00:17:35,220
Ya.

207
00:17:35,304 --> 00:17:37,639
Saya mahu pergi makan sekejap.

208
00:17:37,723 --> 00:17:39,808
Pukul 3 kita masuk mesyuarat.

209
00:17:40,309 --> 00:17:42,144
- Baik, tuan. 
- Okey. Selamat makan.

210
00:17:42,227 --> 00:17:43,604
- Terima kasih. 
- Selamat makan.

211
00:17:47,649 --> 00:17:50,569
- Awak rasa dia dengar? 
- Sudah tentu dia dengar.

212
00:17:50,652 --> 00:17:51,904
- Habis awak. 
- Sial.

213
00:17:51,987 --> 00:17:54,323
Malang nasib kita di balai ini.

214
00:17:54,406 --> 00:17:55,407
Sial.

215
00:18:02,206 --> 00:18:04,124
Semasa kami soal Kim Young-ho,

216
00:18:04,208 --> 00:18:07,628
katanya dia beli sangkar 
pada pukul 5 petang hari itu.

217
00:18:07,711 --> 00:18:11,298
Kemudian, dia keluar minum 
dengan kawan dia sampai pukul 11.

218
00:18:11,381 --> 00:18:13,675
- Ada saksi. 
- Sangkar?

219
00:18:13,759 --> 00:18:17,638
Kim bekalkan bahan 
untuk buat sup berkhasiat.

220
00:18:18,597 --> 00:18:22,101
Wanita simpanan Yang Jae-seok 
berbual dengan dia waktu itu.

221
00:18:22,184 --> 00:18:25,395
Tapi dia di rumah keluarga dia 
di Uijeongbu.

222
00:18:26,063 --> 00:18:28,524
Kang Hong-sik, pemilik agensi penyiasatan

223
00:18:28,607 --> 00:18:31,568
meninggalkan pejabat 
di Seoul pada lewat malam.

224
00:18:32,402 --> 00:18:33,487
Jumpa senjata?

225
00:18:33,570 --> 00:18:37,908
Ya, kami jumpa kelongsong peluru 
berdekatan mayat.

226
00:18:38,492 --> 00:18:41,578
Ia pelet senapang patah, 
buatan Remington, Amerika.

227
00:18:41,662 --> 00:18:45,582
Kita perlu cari orang di sekitar 
yang memiliki senapang memburu.

228
00:18:45,666 --> 00:18:48,585
Ya, kami dah cari, 
tapi tiada sesiapa memilikinya.

229
00:18:48,669 --> 00:18:51,755
Lagipun, kawasan itu bukan tempat memburu.

230
